How to start the application
============================
1. Start com.github.networking.server.Server
2. Start com.github.networking.client.Client

Protocol used for communication:
Client sends a message to the server:
1. "<client " + name + "> Hello Server"
Server responds with:
1. "<server> Hello Client\n"
2. "SIGTERM"

When server sends "SIGTERM" signal, the client closes the connection.

How to build with maven 3
=========================
1. cd to Networking dir
2. mvn clean install
